reviewText: roy is great anywhere you find it.
I am a collector of Roy Rogers Movies
I love Roy Rogers movies and have since I was a little girl.  Thank you for making them available so inexpensively and the orders come quickly and in good condition.

Absolutely love this DVD.  Love both Eyes of Texas and Grand Canyon Trail.  Funny moments with action mixed it on both.  Had seen Grand Canyon Trail on TV but the one on this DVD had so much of the edited parts put back in it was like watching a completely new movie!
